data.description: What a wonderful home for the next phase of your life in the beautiful gated community of Carolina Trace featuring two 18 Hole Golf Courses, Swim/Tennis Facilities, and a 315 Acre Lake for Boating and Fishing.  This move-in ready, open and airy ranch with Vaulted Ceiling features Solid Hardwood Flooring in Liv/Din and all Bedrm areas. A Gorgeous Updated Kitchen with Custom Tile Floor, Stainless Steel Appliances and Cabinets galore. LOOK AT ALL THAT COUNTER SPACE! Open Liv/Din  area leads to large SunRm with New Full-Wall, Energy Efficient Insulated Glass Windows! Step from the SunRm into the HUGE Natural Wood Screened Porch for great outdoor living. The Master Suite features and updated BathRm with a Lg Tiled Walk-In Shower. The 2nd Full Bath also Updated with Tiled Tub/Shower and Floor. The most unique feature is the Loft over Bdrm 2  that offers bright daylight space for Library, Den, Artist Studio, Hobbies/Crafts, etc. Laurel Thicket has its own Pool/Tennis facilities for Residents.
